item.title: 8 stats that show why beach volleyball is the best
item.description:
8 stats that show why beach volleyball is the best

Beach volleyball players would dwarf most of the NBA

It’s fast, it’s thrilling, it’s tough and here’s why it could be your new favourite sport.

item.title: April Ross: Insider Her Training Routine
item.description:
April Ross: Insider Her Training Routine

If you’ve ever seen an Olympic beach volleyball player, it’s probably pretty clear that they work hard at getting fit — you just might not realize how hard. For April Ross,silver medalistat the 2012 Olympic Games in London, and a contender for the gold in the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio, it’s all aboutbuilding strength.
